description: The Zaku I is the original incarnation of the Zaku, produced a few years before the start of the war. Now considered obsolete, it`s used only by non-combat units like the supply corps. One of these primitive Zakus is assigned to Lieutenant Gadem`s Papua-class supply ship, and the old veteran recklessly takes it into battle against the Gundam.
name: MS-05 Zaku I
